title: So_NoTORIous
description:
So NoTORIous is a sitcom on VH1, loosely based on the life of Tori Spelling. The series debuted on April 2, 2006 and despite lasting only ten episodes, received substantial acclaim from critics.

Episodes

1. "Plucky" (April 2, 2006)
2. "Whole" (April 2, 2006)
3. "Street" (April 9, 2006)
4. "Accommodating" (April 16, 2006)
5. "Jealous" (April 23, 2006)
6. "Cursed" (April 23, 2006)
7. "Relaxed" (April 30, 2006)
8. "Charitable" (May 7,2006)
9. "Soulful" (May 14, 2006)
10. "Canadian" (June 1, 2006)

Cast
    * Tori Spelling (Herself)
    * Loni Anderson (Kiki Spelling)
    * James Carpinello (Pete)
    * Brennan Hesser (Janey)
    * Zachary Quinto (Sasan)
    * Jeanetta Arnette (Ruthie Rose)
    * Cleo King (Nanny)
    * Joanna Sanchez (Vilma)
    * Natalija Nogulich (Touca)
    * Brian George (Omid)
    * Ariel Winter (Little Tori)
